{
  "texts": [
    "(3) Empirically, we corroborate the effectiveness of InfoPO on seven benchmarks.",
    "The results demonstrate that InfoPO can significantly outperform previous preference optimization methods.",
    "Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback.",
    "Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback (RLHF) is highly effective in aligning Large Language Models (LLMs) with human preferences (Ouyang et al., 2022; Christiano et al., 2017).",
    "In RLHF, a reward model is trained from human preference data to map responses to a scalar reward, aligning a policy using RL algorithms such as PPO (Schulman et al., 2017)."
  ]
}